    "title": "Line of file",
    "description": "Returns a specific line of a file.\nBe carefull: when you remove a content from a line, it uses regex! So if you're using special chars as \":\" or \"()\" it will convert it in regex.\nUses \"\\\" before the character to avoid that.",
